    "Multimodal action recognitionMultimodal action recognition employs multi-stream approaches to incorporate different modalities.",
    "Motivated by successes in image classification, CNNs have also been applied in different visual action recognition works, where several approaches have been designed to gain the benefits of appearance information.",
